data.description: Welcome home to Spruce Meadow in Woodhaven Village. This energy wise ICI built home will not disappoint. Block construction with brick paver driveway and upgraded lighting, fans and blinds throughout the home. Prefer a fenced backyard? Already done for you and ready to enjoy. You'll appreciate the kitchen in the open floor plan space which includes upgraded 42'' cabinets with under cabinet lighting, pull outs, soft close drawers, custom subway title backsplash, and granite countertops. The oversized 4th bedroom with large closet is perfect for playroom, guest bedroom, office, or cozy movie room. Schedule your showing today.
